race.comment: FERINO (4) resumes here but has won when fresh before and has revved up for this with a recent easy trial. Drawn to get a cosy run in transit from the inside alley and can run a big race while fresh. IVY DEXSTRESS (5) will be at peak fitness now fourth run back from the break and gets the reliable Gollan/Lang combination. Expecting a strong performance despite the wide draw. DIAMOND EPIC (3) is yet to miss a quinella spot in three runs around this circuit and gets a stack of weight off with the 3kg claim. Right in the mix. SMART SHAZZA (6) gets gun hoop Maloney on top and shouldn't be underestimated.
